text: Montchevreuil is a commune in the Oise department in northern France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Fresneaux- Montchevreuil (the seat) and Bachivillers.Arrêté préfectoral 26 December 2018 ==See also== * Communes of the Oise department ==References== Category:Communes of Oise Category:States and territories established in 2019 Category:Populated places established in 2019
title: Montchevreuil
